      </textblock>
    </study_pop>
    <sampling_method>Non-Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients with significant illness of the distal thoracal aorta (distal
             Aortic-dissection; TAA; penetrated ulcer; covered perforation; traumatically
             transection of the distal thoracal aorta) including those that receive an endovascular
             stent or an open surgical operation.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Missing signed informed consent
      </textblock>
